comments: If I knew I was allowed to take notes, I would have! I noticed a consistent pattern in the name of the shapes (beginning of the word) and a pattern in the color (end of the word) but with some exceptions for the colors, it seemed. Also sometimes consonants in the middle of the word were doubled and sometimes they were not. It took me some time to realize I also had to take into account the color of the object (at first I thought only the shape mattered). The difficult aspect of the task was the exceptions and the fact that everything was going very fast. I didn't have enough time to properly see the correction made to my answers and to pause, think, and make sense of it all.
